# VitePress build output + cache
.vitepress/dist/
.vitepress/cache/

# Generated, but tracked: contributing/index.md (synced from /CONTRIBUTING.md)
# and reference/changelog.md (aggregated from packages/*/CHANGELOG.md) are kept
# under version control so a fresh clone has working dead-link resolution. The
# `predev` / `build:sync` hook regenerates them on every run.

# llms artefacts are generated on every build and should not be committed
public/llms.txt
public/llms-api.txt
public/llms-full.txt
